.rule_6_6_1_5_ensure_lockout_period_is_set_to_at_least_30_minutes

Reference: (https://www.juniper.net/documentation/en_US/junos/topics/reference/configur
ation-statement/lockout-period-edit-system-login-retry-options.html)
(https://www.juniper.net/documentation/en_US/junos/topics/reference/comman
d-summary/clear-system-login-lockout.html)
Authentication (https://www.nist.gov/publications/guide-general-server-security)

Remediation: Configure the time users should be locked out using the following command under the
[edit system] hierarchy:
[edit system]
user@host#set login retry-options lockout-period 30

